00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:01.980
Redheads aren't going extinct.

00:00:01.980 --> 00:00:04.909
They aren't soulless-- well,
any more than anyone else is,

00:00:04.909 --> 00:00:06.450
scientifically
speaking-- and they've

00:00:06.450 --> 00:00:09.060
been around for a long time.

00:00:09.060 --> 00:00:14.740
